  "description": "A vulnerability was detected in D-Link DNS-120, DNR-202L, DNS-315L, DNS-320, DNS-320L, DNS-320LW, DNS-321, DNR-322L, DNS-323, DNS-325, DNS-326, DNS-327L, DNR-326, DNS-340L, DNS-343, DNS-345, DNS-726-4, DNS-1100-4, DNS-1200-05 and DNS-1550-04 up to 20260205. Impacted is the function cgi_portforwarding_add/cgi_portforwarding_del/cgi_portforwarding_modify/cgi_portforwarding_add_scan/cgi_dhcpd_lease/cgi_ddns/cgi_ip/cgi_dhcpd of the file /cgi-bin/network_mgr.cgi. The manipulation results in command injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit is now public and may be used.",
